'''Album yar''' waa album duuban oo gaaban ah ama [[Rikoorkii dheerayd|rikoor ciyaar dheer (LP)]], badiyaa wuxuu ku iibiyaa qiimo ka hooseeya album loo tixgelin doono dherer buuxa.  Way ka duwan tahay [[Ciyaar la dheereeyey|ciyaar la dheereeyey (EP)]]-ga sababtoo ah waxaa ku jira raadad badan iyo dherer socod oo xoogaa ka dheer.

Koonfur Kuuriya, album yar ({{ko-hhrm|hangul=미니앨범|rr=}}) waa nooc ka mid ah sii deynta muusikada oo ka kooban 5-7 heesood. Way ka gaaban tahay [[Album|album buuxa]] laakiin waxay ka dheer tahay [[hal album]].<ref>{{Cite web|date=2012-05-04|title=미니앨범? EP앨범? 제대로 알고 듣자-!!|url=https://koreancontent.kr/619|access-date=2021-07-04|website=한국콘텐츠진흥원 상상발전소}}</ref> Caadi ahaan waxay la mid tahay ciyaar la dheereeyey,<ref>{{Citation|title=SuperM: The 1st Mini Album - SuperM {{!}} Songs, Reviews, Credits {{!}} AllMusic|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/superm-the-1st-mini-album-superm-mw0003314271|language=en|access-date=2021-07-04}}</ref> si kastaba ha ahaatee, qaybiyaasha muusikada qaarkood ayaa laga yaabaa inay u kala saaraan albums yar oo leh 7 ama in ka badan heesaha album ahaan.<ref>{{Citation|title=[&] by LOONA|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/1574080252|language=en-US|access-date=2021-07-04}}</ref> 

